mismothering
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:the unsuccessful re-pairing of ewes and lambs following a muster etc.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
